The '''Mozart Medal''' ({{lang-de|'''Mozart-Medaille'''|links=no}}) is an award administered by the [[Mozarteum International Foundation]]. It derives its name from [[Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart]]. The medal is available in three metal types: gold, silver, bronze.
==Recipients== ===Golden=== * [[Lilli Lehmann]], 1914<ref>{{cite web |last=Hinterberger |first=Julia |date=December 2012 |title=Lilli Lehmann – Arbeitsschwerpunkt Salzburger Musikgeschichte |url=https://www.uni-mozarteum.at/apps/app_ck/ckuserfiles/18725/files/Lehmann%2C%20Lilli.pdf |work=Universität Mozarteum |location=Salzburg |access-date=26 August 2018}}</ref> * Max Ott, 1918 * [[Hermann Abert]], 1927 * Friedrich Gehmacher, 1933 * [[Hermann Zilcher]], 1941 * [[Ludwig Schiedermair]], 1942 * [[Alfred Einstein]], 1949 * [[Georges de Saint-Foix]], 1949 * [[Bernhard Paumgartner]], 1951 * [[Vienna Philharmonic]], 1956 * [[Bruno Walter]], 1956 * [[Karl Böhm]], 1956 * Christian Bösmüller, 1957 * Friedrich Gehmacher, 1968 * Richard Spängler, 1985 * [[Sándor Végh]], 1991 * Takahide Sakurai, 1995 * [[Norio Ohga]], 1995 * [[David Woodley Packard]], 2002 * Heinz Wiesmüller, 2003 * Wolfgang Rehm, 2006 * Friedrich Gehmacher jr., 2006 * [[Nikolaus Harnoncourt]], 2011<ref>{{cite web |last= |first= |date=2011 |title=Verleihung der Goldenen Mozart-Medaille an Nikolaus Harnoncourt |url=https://www.harnoncourt.info/goldene-mozart-medaille-fuer-nikolaus-harnoncourt/ |work=harnoncourt.info |location= |publisher= |access-date=18 July 2018}}</ref> * [[András Schiff]], 2012 * [[Milos Forman]], 2013 * [[Alfred Brendel]], 2014<ref>{{cite news |last=Kainberger |first=Hedwig |date=28 January 2014 |title=Alfred Brendel: "Verneige mich vor dem Wunder Mozart" |url=https://www.sn.at/salzburg/kultur/alfred-brendel-verneige-mich-vor-dem-wunder-mozart-3997045 |work=[[Salzburger Nachrichten]] |location= |access-date=18 July 2018}}</ref> * [[Mitsuko Uchida]], 2015<ref>{{cite news |last=Kriechbaum |first=Reinhard |date= 27 January 2016 |title=Der denkbar quirligste Lebens-Geist |url=https://www.wienerzeitung.at/themen_channel/musik/klassik_oper/797644_Der-denkbar-quirligste-Lebens-Geist.html |work=[[Wiener Zeitung]] |location= |access-date=17 July 2018}}</ref> * [[Mozarteum Orchestra Salzburg]], 2015 *